
   TOY DECODER
   ===========

Author:  Robert Michaels

date:  Dec 5, 2013 

purpose:  A light-weight test of the design concept for the OO decoder.

Details of the OO decoder:
    http://userweb.jlab.org/~rom/oodecoder_nov13.pdf
    to be updated before the Dec Hall A Software Mtg

Content

  main:   tstoy_main.C

  Seven new classes

     ToyCodaDecoder     (inherits from THaEvData)

     ToyEvtTypeHandler   (abstract base class)  
        ToyPhysicsEvtHandler   (inherits from ToyEvtTypeHandler)
        ToyScalerEvtHandler    (inherits from ToyEvtTypeHandler)
     
     ToyModule    
        ToyFastbusModule       (inherits from ToyModule) 
        ToyModuleX             (inherits from ToyModule) 


   With Small Modifications to 

        THaEvData
             use crate map to add "ToyModule" to a crate and slot
             new LoadData method to allow modules to load the data.
 
        THaSlotData
             new member fModule   (a "ToyModule" belongs to a slot
                                             in a crate)
             note to self:  need copy c'tor for modules        
 

